---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base
  title="Uvjeti korištenja / Terms of Service"
  description="Uvjeti korištenja CheckinPack aplikacije."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Uvjeti korištenja</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">Terms of Service · Posljednje ažuriranje / Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-8">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Usluga / The service</h2>
        <p>
          CheckinPack je alat koji vlasnicima kratkoročnog smještaja pomaže u pripremi podataka za
          eVisitor prijavu gostiju i komunikaciji s gostima putem digitalnog vodiča.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">
          CheckinPack is a tool that helps short-term accommodation owners prepare guest data for
          eVisitor registration and communicate with guests via a digital welcome guide.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Odgovornost za eVisitor prijavu / eVisitor responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          CheckinPack priprema i organizira podatke gostiju radi olakšavanja eVisitor prijave.
          <strong>Vlasnik smještaja ostaje jedino odgovoran za točnost i pravodobnost prijave gostiju
          u eVisitor sustav.</strong> CheckinPack ne podnosi prijave u ime vlasnika niti ne garantira
          usklađenost s važećim propisima.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">
          CheckinPack prepares and organises guest data to assist with eVisitor registration.
          <strong>The accommodation owner remains solely responsible for the accuracy and timeliness
          of guest registration in the eVisitor system.</strong> CheckinPack does not submit
          registrations on behalf of owners, nor does it guarantee regulatory compliance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Pretplata i plaćanje / Subscription and payment</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Besplatni plan dostupan je bez vremenskog ograničenja uz funkcionalna ograničenja. / The free plan is available indefinitely with functional limits.</li>
          <li>Pro plan naplaćuje se €5 za 3 mjeseca ili €20 godišnje, putem Stripe platne platforme. / The Pro plan is billed at €5/3 months or €20/year via Stripe.</li>
          <li>Pretplatu možete otkazati u bilo kojem trenutku iz postavki računa. / You may cancel your subscription at any time from account settings.</li>
          <li>Nakon otkazivanja vraćate se na besplatni plan; podaci ostaju sačuvani. / After cancellation, you revert to the free plan; your data is retained.</li>
          <li>Povrat novca nije automatski, ali kontaktirajte nas ako imate opravdan zahtjev. / Refunds are not automatic — contact us if you have a legitimate request.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Podaci gostiju / Guest data</h2>
        <p>
          Vlasnik smještaja odgovoran je za prikupljanje suglasnosti gostiju za obradu osobnih podataka
          u svrhu zakonske prijave. CheckinPack pruža tehničku infrastrukturu za tu obradu.
          Podaci gostiju automatski se brišu 30 dana nakon odjave.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">
          The accommodation owner is responsible for obtaining guest consent for personal data processing
          for the purpose of legal registration. CheckinPack provides the technical infrastructure for
          that processing. Guest data is automatically deleted 30 days after checkout.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Ograničenje odgovornosti / Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          CheckinPack se pruža "kakav jest" bez jamstava dostupnosti ili točnosti.
          U maksimalnoj mjeri dopuštenoj zakonom, odgovornost CheckinPacka ograničena je na iznos
          koji ste platili za uslugu u posljednjih 12 mjeseci.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">
          CheckinPack is provided "as is" without warranties of availability or accuracy.
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, CheckinPack's liability is limited to the amount
          you paid for the service in the past 12 months.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Promjene uvjeta / Changes to terms</h2>
        <p>
          Zadržavamo pravo izmjene ovih uvjeta. O značajnim promjenama obavijestit ćemo vas e-poštom
          najmanje 14 dana unaprijed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">
          We reserve the right to modify these terms. We will notify you of significant changes by
          email at least 14 days in advance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">7. Kontakt / Contact</h2>
        <p>Za pitanja vezana uz uvjete: <a href="mailto:pinjamar@gmail.com" class="text-brand">pinjamar@gmail.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
